## Quick Start

```bash
# Add a tool from GitHub releases
shimexe add uv --path https://github.com/astral-sh/uv/releases/download/0.7.13/uv-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip --add-system-path

# Use it directly
uv --version

# Or through shimexe run
shimexe run uv --version
```

